{"tid":2156053,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔好再買壹傳媒股票，蝕死你呀","createTime":"2020-08-14T07:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T07:44:35.000Z","uid":278298,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3c2a6992b3f869071d2564bb9c27af6af2ca902d","tid":2156053,"uid":278298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:38:43.000Z","msg":"邊個會咁講呀？咪肥佬黎囉～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請問有邊個老闆會咁呢? 大家一定要繼續撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200814/BJBJSVBQO5EZ7LQCRKHCWSMJGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200814%2FBJBJSVBQO5EZ7LQCRKHCWSMJGI%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=8f6ff4d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200814%2FBJBJSVBQO5EZ7LQCRKHCWSMJGI%2F&h=1d859769\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200814/BJBJSVBQO5EZ7LQCRKHCWSMJGI/</a><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英接受《彭博》訪問時表示，警告投資者，不要買入壹傳媒的股票，因為該公司的基本面無法支持最近的上漲趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n他表示：「收入很少的人只想表達自己的憤怒並表示對我們公司的支持...每個人都買了一點兒。那就變得很多了，並推高了股價。我告訴人們『不要這麼做，不要這麼做，因為你會虧錢的』。」"},{"pid":"b29045655bcc6652a38520d802bbadf0e9da03f4","tid":2156053,"uid":258356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"撐蘋果又有閒錢，應該訂閱、買報紙、落廣告<br />\n<br />\n買蘋果股票，只係支持緊沽貨個個人，蘋果無任何實際得益的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}